524
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:43,120
Abang, saya bukan sengaja
nak kacau awak.

525
00:36:43,630 --> 00:36:44,670
Namun, saya ada hal yang

526
00:36:44,670 --> 00:36:46,320
kena bincang dengan tuan puteri
secara berseorangan.

527
00:36:46,870 --> 00:36:47,520
Bolehkah...

528
00:36:47,520 --> 00:36:48,190
Tak boleh.

529
00:36:50,080 --> 00:36:50,800
Tan'er.

530
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:52,910
Tentunya adik datang lewat
atas urusan penting.

531
00:36:53,190 --> 00:36:54,320
Memandangkan kamu bincang sesuatu,

532
00:36:54,430 --> 00:36:55,630
