533
00:36:55,870 --> 00:36:56,760
Terima kasih.

534
00:36:58,040 --> 00:37:00,950
Jing Xin, awak menemani abang.

535
00:37:03,040 --> 00:37:03,670
Baik.

536
00:37:17,560 --> 00:37:18,360
